  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age 18-65

          -  Chronic Pain patient or healthy control

          -  Ability to perform the experimental task

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  MRI contraindication (metal implants, claustrophobia, pregnant or planning to become
